============================
 Pipeline-Config Change Log
============================

All changes by Steve Purkis <spurkis@epn.nu> unless otherwise stated.

v0.05
    +	added cleanups pipeline support
    +	YAML now required [reported by Jean-Michel Hiver]
    +	updated dependencies

v0.04
    +	fixed dependencies in Build.PL

v0.03
    +	added search packages support
    +	moved to Module::Build
    +	now recognize .yml files as yaml
    +	all pm's now use $P::Config::VERSION, cvs revision in $REVISION  

v0.02
    +	moved *Error classes to their correct location
    +	$confg->debug now propagates through to parsers
    +	error text now being reported properly

v0.01
    +	project created

